    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-06-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-06-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="284"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d284">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Sir F.
                        Bruce</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                >Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-06-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 14, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir;</hi> I have been requested by the president of the
                    Soldiers’ National Cemetery, at Gettysburg, Pennsylvania, to extend to you an
                    invitation to attend the ceremonies of laying the corner-stone of the monument
                    to the memory of the soldiers who fell on the battle-field of Gettysburg, which
                    are to take place on the 4th of July next.</p>
                <p>The ceremonies cannot fail to be interesting, and it is hoped that you may find
                    it convenient to accept the invitation to be present on that occasion.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, with the highest consideration, sir, your obedient
                    servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir Frederick W. A. Bruce</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                            >&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
